@startuml
!include _theme.puml

title Monitor — Local Deployment / Integration Topology
caption Containers, local services, and development routing used by the project

node "Developer Workstation" {
  artifact "Browser" as Browser

  node "Frontend Dev Server\nlocalhost:3000" as NextDev {
    artifact "Next.js app\nfrontend/" as NextApp
  }

  node "Backend App\nlocalhost:8080" as SpringApp {
    artifact "Monitor Spring Boot JAR" as Jar
  }
}

node "Docker Compose Network\nmonitor-net" {
  database "Oracle XE 11g\n1521" as Oracle
  node "Zookeeper\n2181" as Zookeeper
  queue "Kafka\n9092 / 29092" as Kafka
  node "Kafka Connect / Debezium\n8083" as Debezium
}

cloud "SMTP / Groupwise" as SMTP

Browser --> NextDev : HTTP UI access
NextDev --> SpringApp : rewrite /api/*\n(frontend/next.config.js)
Browser --> SpringApp : optional direct API access

SpringApp --> Kafka : Kafka consumer
SpringApp --> SMTP : mail alerts
Debezium --> Kafka : CDC events
Oracle --> Debezium : database changes
Kafka --> Zookeeper : broker coordination

note right of NextDev
Local development rewrite:
/api/:path* -> http://localhost:8080/api/:path*
end note

note right of SpringApp
Main runtime ports:
- frontend dev: 3000
- backend HTTP/SSE: 8080
- Kafka host access: 9092
- Debezium REST: 8083
- Oracle: 1521
end note
@enduml

